 f'(x) = (p-1)(x-1)(x+1)^{p-2} + (x+1)^{p-1} - p x^{p-1} \>, 
 f'(x) = (p-1)(x-1)(x+1)^{p-2} + x^{p-1}\left(\left(1+\frac{1}{x}\right)^{p-1} - p\right)  \> . 
